{"type": "article", "id": 3389, "title": "迷你室内篮球架", "description": "", "date": "2014-11-10T07:44:36Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 6, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606052327349t6YrycwnzTvFPdX.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t来自洛杉矶的配件品牌 Killspencer 日前带来了一款迷你室内篮球架，希望能给篮球爱好者制造一片能在家里或是办公室实现的小型篮球空间。这款迷你篮球架既可以挂于横梁之上，亦可以挂在墙上，提供「Classic」与「Special」两种版本的选择，前者由黑色的枫木篮板搭配黑色皮革篮网与黑色涂层的篮筐组成，后者则经过了镀金的装饰，透出奢华风情。定价 795 美元，<a href=\"http://killspencer.com/indoor-mini-basketball-kit.html\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232732hxFt4vLJyG3PX8B0.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232732ktPeXOxIWfL71lym.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.6671875\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232732uWHr2mCtgYQpo0Xq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160605232733z6NUBs7p53iQGVc2.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.8\" data-format=\"jpeg\"> \r\n</p>\n\n\n"}